## 0. How to use this document

This is the source of truth for **how we build UI** in this product. Every new component, page, or PR should be checked against Section 3 (Design System) and Section 5 (Engineering Rules) before merge. Section 8 is the week-by-week execution plan for the first 4 months, with the remaining 8 months at milestone-level.

